iteria\n    50\t\n    51\t- loop daemon state is visible without opening a terminal\n    52\t- loop logs can be watched or tailed from the managed workflow\n    53\t- one card can enter loop mode with a clear interval setting\n    54\t- start / stop / restart actions are available in the extension itself\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
